      <title>泰国延长印度、台湾游客免签证计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/thailand-extends-visa-waiver-plan-for-indian-taiwanese-tourists</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国内阁批准了一项计划，将印度和台湾游客的免签计划再延长六个月，因为这个东南亚国家寻求增加外国游客数量以支撑其疲软的经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/thailand-extends-visa-waiver-plan-for-indian-taiwanese-tourists</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 08:47:19 GMT</pubDate>
